<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/confuse_ray">Confuse Ray</a> is a Ghost-type equivalent.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/swagger">Swagger</a> is an equivalent move, but boosts the target's Attack.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/sweet_kiss">Sweet Kiss</a> is an equivalent move, but has 20% more accuracy.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/teeter_dance">Teeter Dance</a> is an equivalent move, but confuses all targets.</p>